data.description: Check out this 3 bedroom, 2 bath, brick home situated right in town in Shipman. Large living room. Spacious eat in kitchen. Appliances stay. Main floor family room/sun room measures 19ft by 19ft. Attached 1 car garage. Main floor laundry room/utility room/half bath. NEW A/C AND WATER HEATER IN 2023. Electric baseboard heat. Public water. Publicly maintained septic. Schedule an appointment to see this one in person.
